{{Rough translation}}'''卡羅爾·克羅斯'''（{{lang-pl|Karol Kłos}}；{{bd|1989年|8月8日}}）是一位[[波蘭|波蘭]]排球運動員。他也代表波蘭國家排球隊參賽，參加了2014年世界排球錦標賽<ref>[http://www.fivb.org/viewPressRelease.asp?No=49498&Language=en#.VCAG_qIu6ho ''Poland win second World Championship title at home''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fivb.org/viewPressRelease.asp?No=49498&Language=en#.VCAG_qIu6ho |date=20181005153335 }} - fivb.org - 21-09-2014</ref><ref>[http://www.fivb.org/viewPressRelease.asp?No=49500&Language=en#.VCAHAaIu6ho ''Poland put an end to the reign of Brazil''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fivb.org/viewPressRelease.asp?No=49500&Language=en#.VCAHAaIu6ho |date=20181229031625 }} - fivb.org - 21-09-2014</ref><ref>[http://www.plusliga.pl/news/id/9914 ''FIVB MŚ Polska 2014: Polska ze złotym medalem''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.plusliga.pl/news/id/9914 |date=20190708110420 }} - plusliga.pl - 21-09-2014</ref><ref>[http://poland2014.fivb.org/en/news/poland-in-dreamland-and-in-dream-team?id=49497 ''Poland in dreamland and in Dream Team''] {{Wayback|url=http://poland2014.fivb.org/en/news/poland-in-dreamland-and-in-dream-team?id=49497 |date=20200919124402 }} - poland2014.fivb.org - 21-09-2014</ref>，並為波蘭獲得了世錦賽金牌。

